  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients undergoing elective nephrectomy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  contraindication against pregabalin

          -  creatinine &gt; 2.0 mg/dl

          -  GGT &gt;165, AST &gt;105, ALT &gt;135

          -  peptic Ulcus

          -  haemorrhagic diathesis

          -  angina pectoris, myocardial infarction

          -  stroke

          -  bronchial asthma

          -  opioid abuse
      </textblock>
